      "settings": {
        "background_color": "#fbf9ee",
        "heading": "The cut",
        "text": "<p>The cut of a diamond describes the quality of its facets, that is, the different parts of a diamond. The cut is the most important factor in determining the brilliance of a diamond, a good cut can brighten and sparkle, while a poorly cut diamond can appear lifeless and dark. It is about not cutting the diamond too shallow, or too deep. All diamond shapes have different ideal dimensions.</p>",
